# localskills_scim_tokens (Data Source)

Lists all SCIM provisioning tokens for a team. Token secret values are not included; only metadata such as name, creation date, and last-used timestamp is returned.

Use this data source to audit SCIM tokens, check expiration dates, or verify that provisioning tokens are active and in use.

